Class Anime

java.lang.Object
AnimeDatabase.Anime
public class Anime extends Object
Represents an anime entity in the Anime Database Management System.

  • Constructor Details

    • Anime

      public Anime(String title, String genre, int episodes, double rating, String studio, int startYear, int endYear, String type)
      Constructor to initialize an Anime object with specified values.
      Parameters:
      title - the title of the anime
      genre - the genre of the anime
      episodes - the number of episodes of the anime
      rating - the rating of the anime
      studio - the studio that produced the anime
      startYear - the year the anime started airing
      endYear - the year the anime ended airing
      type - the type of the anime (e.g., TV, Movie, OVA, ONA)
